Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見妳也會記得我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕我會逐漸習慣於戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得自己會變成另一種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實大家都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許沒有人可以永不改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們確實存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就存在於這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你再怎麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會永遠記得一騎的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
